{"tid":1630734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修有原則，咁獅鳥可唔可以都有分類法？","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T02:09:57.000Z","uid":111907,"like":70,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"89163a2048a3384e2475e5e76568fdf6ed4a6b21","tid":1630734,"uid":111907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:30:28.000Z","msg":"純語言挑釁：<br />\nAttention seeker，唔好理佢/唱生日歌送走佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n影大頭/輕微威脅行為：<br />\n制服佢/逼佢del晒啲相/如果係中國人就可以幫佢平反六四/髮型師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚴重威脅行為（持武器/揸車撞人）：獅鳥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n純建議，歡迎討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49df402dced27518460b4c3f6ba1f93a9e8eb12f","tid":1630734,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"d06d6fddbb4eded5560a705d1bc23dae329a7179","tid":1630734,"uid":111907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:31:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"78e7a677d31f7b41b0ff134534b143258afa4258","tid":1630734,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:32:28.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ca374aba6d44197f9f2aaedc1429c331f7005ddc","tid":1630734,"uid":111907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2e8cf6d4cefe90401d1fae654f1e3f723fde9c96","tid":1630734,"uid":111907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:32:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8544cf8466e662603791f53fa0a42a3e1ca464d3","tid":1630734,"uid":111907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583359f592c775138369b198c98ae3d7a42733fa","tid":1630734,"uid":111907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d9055529a65e7d652da3e912b75646f0924e13","tid":1630734,"uid":111907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617666f10cb615a3cbc880d334018ae3f3c0b50d","tid":1630734,"uid":111907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10